---
title: Easy Moroccan Pork Kofta & Cucumber Salad  with Rapid Rice
description: It’s pork koftas and fluffy rice tonight, and we know it’s going to be a new favourite when you get a taste of that Moroccan curry
glaze! All you need is some crunch from the cucumber salad and there you have it - another home-run for weeknight dinners.
